Name: Mighty Planes
Title: Twin Otter
Desc: The Twin Otter is found anywhere rugged reliability and short-take-off-and-landing are needed.
LongDescription: The Twin Otter is found around the world in jungles, deserts, mountains, the Arctic, and anywhere rugged reliability and short-take-off-and-landing are needed; powered by twin turboprop engines, the Twin Otter manoeuvres like a bird.
